<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Flower-de-luce" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Flower-de-luce,</orth> the white lily: <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.127" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 127</bibl>. Armorial emblem of France: <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.1.80" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 1, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.2.99" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 99</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B V, 1, 11</bibl>. Hence King Henry calls Princess Katharine so: <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.224" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 224</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>